QuestData.Title: A New Architect
QuestData.Description:
The architects prototype designs to fulfill the purposes of the First Ones.
This archive contained many such designs.
A number of design entries are lost or corrupted due to the Maw invasion.
An untouched design lattice and tools are detected nearby. The mortal will retrieve them to begin the synthesis process.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Cervid Lattice and $2oa Protoform Tools and bring them to the Servitor Interface in the Protoform Repository.
QuestData.RewardText:
Success.
The Protoform Repository is now restored.
